reviewText: Anything on the IMMORTAL label from Holland is a BOOTLEG, usually of poor quality! You've been warned.......
Video quality for a dvd was awful and I think the 5.1 surround sound was fake.
Excellent concert. Clapton, Page, and Beck on stage together! Doesn't get any better. Unfortunately,  the video quality is very poor. Concert from the 1980's, so, not unexpected.
Given the age of the original recording, the visual may not have been the greatest, but the music was excellent.  This was thoroughly enjoyable.  What fantastic musicians.

I bought this DVD about a year ago, this is a very poor South American version. They turned the full-frame screen into a widescreen format. The picture looks elongated or stretched. There are other versions out there (also South American) but I don't recommend this one, I resold it after I received in excited anticipation but was really disappointed in both the audio & video quality.
